Step 1: Install Ansible on Linux
	-> sudo apt update
	-> sudo apt install ansible -y
	-> ansible --version 
	
Step 2: Set up Ansible Inventory & Configuration
	a) Create a directory
	-> mkdir ansible-cisco
	-> cd ansible-cisco
	b) Create an inventory
	-> nano hosts
	
Step 3: Create the Ansible Playbook
	-> nano get_running_config.yml
	
Step 4: Create Ansible Configuration File
	-> nano ansible.cfg
	
Step 5: Run the Ansible Playbook 
	-> ansible-playbook get_running_config.yml
	
